<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 00:51:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>陷入困境的中国恒大重返法庭进行清算听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/embattled-china-evergrande-back-court-liquidation-hearing-2024-01-28/</link><description>由于投资者和消费者信心低迷仍然是中国经济的主要拖累，开发商的清算裁决可能会震动脆弱的中国资本和房地产市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 23:15:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/embattled-china-evergrande-back-court-liquidation-hearing-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国 PMI 和美联储决定将带来更多欢呼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-28/</link><description>美联储的行动和主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的新闻发布会将主导会议进程。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:49:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>中美本周将就芬太尼前体化学品问题举行会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/first-meeting-us-china-working-group-fentanyl-precursor-chemicals-be-held-2024-01-28/</link><description>一位美国高级官员周日表示，中美芬太尼前体化学品工作组首次联席会议将于周二在北京举行。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 14:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/first-meeting-us-china-working-group-fentanyl-precursor-chemicals-be-held-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国允许菲律宾向争议岛礁派遣部队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-allows-philippines-supply-troops-disputed-reef-2024-01-28/</link><description>中国海警表示，已做出“临时特别安排”，允许菲律宾通过一艘停泊在争议礁石上的二战时期船只向部队运送物资。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 13:08:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-allows-philippines-supply-troops-disputed-reef-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国法案提出后，中国华大智造、GemPharmatech 为自己辩护</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-mgi-tech-gempharmatech-defend-themselves-after-us-bill-proposed-2024-01-28/</link><description>中国华大智造周日表示，作为基因测序行业的上游设备提供商，在美国拟议的生物安全法案将其名字纳入法案后，其业务不涉及数据收集。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 08:23:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-mgi-tech-gempharmatech-defend-themselves-after-us-bill-proposed-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>英国《金融时报》报道，俄罗斯计划建设的通往中国的天然气管道面临施工延误</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-planned-gas-pipeline-china-faces-construction-delay-ft-2024-01-28/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周日报道，蒙古总理奥云额尔登表示，俄罗斯计划于今年启动的通往中国的新西伯利亚力量2号天然气管道的建设可能会被推迟。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 08:08:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-planned-gas-pipeline-china-faces-construction-delay-ft-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国证监会周一起暂停限制性股票借贷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-securities-regulator-suspends-restricted-share-lending-monday-2024-01-28/</link><description>中国证券监管机构周日表示，将从周一起全面暂停限制性股票的出借，这是政策制定者在近期股市大幅下跌后稳定股市的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 07:37:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-securities-regulator-suspends-restricted-share-lending-monday-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国与泰国签署互免签证协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-sign-mutual-visa-waiver-agreements-2024-01-28/</link><description>泰国和中国周日同意免除对方国民的签证要求，以促进受新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 影响的两国之间的旅行和旅游业。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 05:26:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-sign-mutual-visa-waiver-agreements-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>印度远离俄罗斯武器，但仍将保持牢固关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-pivots-away-russian-arms-will-retain-strong-ties-2024-01-28/</link><description>过去20年里，印度武器采购总额超过600亿美元，其中65%是由俄罗斯提供的，但乌克兰战争加速了印度武器基地多元化的动力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 02:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-pivots-away-russian-arms-will-retain-strong-ties-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国和中国高级官员在曼谷讨论台湾和伊朗问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-wang-says-taiwan-issue-biggest-threat-sino-us-ties-2024-01-27/</link><description>在总统乔·拜登和中国领导人习近平预计将于春季通话之前，中美高级官员在曼谷举行坦诚会谈，旨在缓解超级大国之间在台湾和其他问题上的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 15:06:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-wang-says-taiwan-issue-biggest-threat-sino-us-ties-2024-01-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国称日本渔船非法进入钓鱼岛领海</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-japanese-fishing-vessel-illegally-enters-territorial-waters-diaoyu-2024-01-27/</link><description>据中国国家电视台中央电视台周六晚间报道，中国海警称一艘日本渔船和几艘巡逻艇非法进入钓鱼岛领海。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 13:41:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-japanese-fishing-vessel-illegally-enters-territorial-waters-diaoyu-2024-01-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国称王毅与美国沙利文就处理问题进行了“坦诚、富有成果”的会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-wang-us-sullivan-held-candid-fruitful-talks-handling-issues-2024-01-27/</link><description>中国外交部周六表示，中国外交部长王毅与美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文进行了“坦诚、实质性和富有成效的战略沟通”，旨在进一步落实两国领导人对话的承诺。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 13:19:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-wang-us-sullivan-held-candid-fruitful-talks-handling-issues-2024-01-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国的郑对萨巴伦卡的现实检查感到沮丧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/chinas-zheng-downcast-by-sabalenka-reality-check-2024-01-27/</link><description>中国选手郑沁文表示，她对没有展现自己最好的网球水平感到非常失望，因为她在周六的澳大利亚网球公开赛决赛中被萨巴伦卡从罗德·拉沃尔球场击落。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 12:54:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/chinas-zheng-downcast-by-sabalenka-reality-check-2024-01-27/</guid></item><item><title>萨巴伦卡在墨尔本获胜后称赞球队为她的方法增添了疯狂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-hails-team-after-second-australian-open-crown-2024-01-27/</link><description>阿丽娜·萨巴伦卡周六以强势的方式赢得了她的第二个澳大利亚网球公开赛冠军，并赞扬她的教练团队让场外的生活变得有点“疯狂”，以缓解精英级别网球带来的压力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 11:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-hails-team-after-second-australian-open-crown-2024-01-27/</guid></item><item><title>萨巴伦卡力压郑智卫冕澳网冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-overpowers-zheng-retain-australian-open-crown-2024-01-27/</link><description>阿丽娜·萨巴伦卡以绝对统治力的表现成为 11 年来第一位卫冕澳大利亚公开赛冠军的女性，并在周六以她的第二个大满贯冠军向她的对手发出了警告。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 10:39:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-overpowers-zheng-retain-australian-open-crown-2024-01-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>